These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | february | september | january | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, go, billiard
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
4. the person playing snooker is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | snooker  | go    | scrabble | billiard    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, japanese, pakistani, russian
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the russian is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the pakistani##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the doctor is the mexican##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the mexican is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | russian       | japanese  | mexican  | pakistani |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

