.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, water, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking coffee is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sprite | water    | milk  | coffee   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

