.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, time-travel, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, game, swisher, dannemann
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
2. the swisher-smoker is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is the game-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
5. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy     | time-travel | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | swisher | dunhill | dannemann      | game         |

