.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, baking, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, photographer, social-worker
1. the coach is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | filmmaking  | rock-climbing        | baking      | photography          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

