.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, lawyer, teacher
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, siglo, bongani, prince
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the siglo-smoker is not the teacher##6
3. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
6. the prince-smoker is the lawyer##1
7. the bartender is not the prince-smoker##6
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bartender  | lawyer | teacher    | fisherman |
| Transport   | siglo | prince | bongani | fonseca  |

