.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, boat, van, jet-ski
1. the person driving the subway is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
6. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | subway     | jet-ski | boat | van |

