.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, mango, cranberry, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
3. the fan indie is not the person eating cranberry##6
4. the person eating mango is between the fan pop and the person eating cranberry##2
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating mango##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person eating apple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | cranberry | mango    | apple | nectarine |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

