.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
City: boston, hannover, paris, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
2. the person traveling to hannover is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the person traveling to boston is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to hannover and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | new-york | hannover      | boston | paris   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

