.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
House: cape-cod, colonial, ranch-style, townhouse
1. the ranch-style house is not the person drinking water##6
2. the ranch-style house is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the townhouse house is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the colonial house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | water       | hot-chocolate | fanta     | lemonade     |
| Movie-Genre   | cape-cod | ranch-style       | townhouse | colonial |

