.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, volleyball, water-polo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, rock, jazz
1. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the fan blues##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the fan d&b is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
6. the fan jazz is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | lacrosse | basketball | water-polo | volleyball |
| Transport   | rock   | blues       | d&b    | jazz     |

