3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | november    | december | september | october         |
| Sport      | handball | lacrosse | golf          | weightlifting |

