2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the mouse is not the person who likes mauve##6
5. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes black##2
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
8. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | black | amber | mauve | light-blue |
| Pet     | lizard  | fish      | chinchilla  | mouse       |

