.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, july, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
6. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | august  | september   | july | december |

 